title: SIC! SIC! SIC!
html:
SIC! SIC! SIC!

“Then, on July 20, 1969, he and Neil Armstrong made their historic Apollo XI moon walk, becoming the first two humans to set food on another world.” [From the program notes for the 1999 PNC Bank Concert Series with the Philadelphia Orchestra at the Mann Center for the Performing Arts, Charles Dutoit, Artistic Director, Wednesday, July 21, at 8 p.m. Submitted by Jonathan Rockey, Glenside, PA.]
